    "text": "Staffordshire St presents Are the Stones Standing Still, an exhibition-cum-symposium. The weekend event acts as a follow-up to Eastside Project's 2023 If It Thunders on All Fool's Day. \u201cAs England crumbles, arts funding is cut and Starmer\u2019s Labour gain power \u2013 are there new ways of doing? Or are the stones standing still? From the regions to the capital, no one\u2019s watching. Do something.\u201d With performances from Chloe Langlois, Campbell Mcconnell, Ross Hammond, Lolly Adams, Bijan Moosavi, Louise Ashcroft and Chanel Vegas",
